title: Backend Developer
description: I participated in the Fast Track program at Compasso, gaining skills in REST API development with Java and Spring Boot. At Livelo, I contributed to the backoffice, collaborating on the construction of the management system for B2B partners. I performed integrations with AWS services such as S3, SNS, and SQS, and utilized RabbitMQ and Keycloak for messaging and authentication, respectively.
